channel.title: Webclient Error, Think Its To Do With Jar-ring ? (PIC)
channel.description:
Right, i made a decent HTML website yeh, did a tutorial to making a webclient, but the jar-ring bit is not explained at all, they just expect you to know how to do it. Well i don't.
Here's the pic of the error
[IMG]http://i285.photobucket.com/albums/ll63/Silent_CJ/WebclientError.jpg[/img]
It just does that over and over again...
Oh yeh, and heres the code for the archive, ip, and the port.
[code]archive="./signed_client.jar" code="client"> <param name="host" value="Ownedscape123.no-ip.org"> <param name="port" value="43594">[/code]
Anyways, hope someone can help, also, visit my topic in my sig ;)
Thanks :)
